title: #92Noon! Vox in the Box! Evason/Guerin/Russo/Carter/Stalock
description: PA and Nordo are live from the Minnesota Wild's practice at Tria Rink in St. Paul. Top brass, Coach Dean Evason and GM Bill Guerin join. Russo Radio is live in action as well as FSN's Ryan Carter. And catching up with Wild goaltender and his magnificent hair, Alex Stalock.
